#

Grilled Herb-Marinated Chicken with Garlic Mashed Potatoes and Honey-Glazed Carrots

$15
680 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

dairy

Dietary Tags:

high-proteinlow-carb

Tags:

grilledeasycomfort food

Description

Juicy grilled chicken marinated in aromatic herbs, paired with creamy garlic mashed potatoes and sweet honey-glazed carrots for a delightful meal.

Ingredients

  • Chicken breasts: 2 pieces
  • Olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Fresh rosemary: 1 tablespoon, chopped
  • Fresh thyme: 1 tablespoon, chopped
  • Garlic: 3 cloves, minced
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
  • Potatoes: 4 medium, peeled and chopped
  • Butter: 2 tablespoons
  • Milk: 1/4 cup
  • Carrots: 3 medium, sliced
  • Honey: 1 tablespoon
